    "body": "Using the [JavaScript API client](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-client/getting-started/install/javascript/) as you mentioned is what InstantSearch does under the hood. InstantSearch comes handy when you want to build an application and manage the state of the search in your page. From what I understand of your usage, using the [API client](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-client/getting-started/install/javascript/) would be enough.",
